{"tid":862853,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［香港長板聚會]召集所有玩longboard既巴打絲打","createTime":"2018-10-15T07:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T11:32:41.000Z","uid":216717,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5f91c48b5c6ed90f8205b8a0edea2ef931d9dcc4","tid":862853,"uid":216717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:16:01.000Z","msg":"可能係香港第一個最大型既板聚 <br />\n希望今個星期日會見到有踩longboard既你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nIg：docksessionhk<br />\nFacebook: DockSession Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1st DockSession in Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nDockSession是一個活躍於國際的長板活動組織，我們香港有幸於今年參與其中，並邀請到DockSession聖地牙哥地區代表 @joiskwan 參與這次的長板盛事。<br />\n屆時活動將會有Best Freestyle Lines, Best Tricks等比賽，贏得比賽的朋友可獲豐富的獎品！<br />\n比賽完後更有一些團體小遊戲，讓踩長板的朋友們互相認識及有一個愉快和歡樂的聚會。<br />\n<br />\n活動詳情如下：<br />\n2018年10月21日<br />\n下午3時正<br />\n西九龍文化區大馬路 ※參加者請注意安全，穿戴護具。如有任何損傷，本會概不負責<br />\n※如天氣惡劣，本會或考慮另作安排，請留意Facebook及Instagram專頁最新動態<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/Bo8YC-Fl6bi/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1pdit0hlmmkk4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBo8YC-Fl6bi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D1pdit0hlmmkk4&d=RE0JyUklRsIotNln4UT7XSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=97d8207c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBo8YC-Fl6bi%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_share_sheet%26igshid%3D1pdit0hlmmkk4&h=9216ef3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/Bo8YC-Fl6bi/?utm_source=ig_share_sheet&amp;igshid=1pdit0hlmmkk4</a>"},{"pid":"a54eb15570601f45273c859d501bf988f97e20ca","tid":862853,"uid":138564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T07:51:39.000Z","msg":"大家快啲上水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa4ca